{"tid":1742911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（行動po)有關黎明行動既轉型 大家一齊改善 一齊進步","createTime":"2019-11-21T03:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T10:22:40.000Z","uid":124128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d5b0ad4951dc8fe3806429e29e8e79a0369b23","tid":1742911,"uid":124128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"手足們 我有個小小提議 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其係到塞鐵 不如嘗試下和你搭鐵 我地可以扮演類似而家foodpanda咁既角色 務求將運動打入民心 我地戴gear企係每個車門隔離 見人就講早晨（籠絡民意呀！）（gear唔係重點 你帶個口罩都得，最重要係傳遞既意識！）<br />\n<br />\n-唔會擾民 <br />\n-吸引市民眼球，籠絡民意<br />\n-順便可以將抗爭日常化（實現地下化？）<br />\n-狗隻吹我地唔脹？ 而家一街二噁英 帶個濾咀好正常姐<br />\n-和理非 大人細路一齊參與又得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-要持之以恆（預左長期戰？）<br />\n<br />\n而家對家最想我地民鬥民 同埋武力抗爭，點解我地要順佢地意？ <br />\n<br />\n對家武力只會無限升級，我地得啲19汽油彈炸記住<br />\n<br />\n我地更加唔會搶鎗，殺狗 <br />\n<br />\n咁打黎根本無意思<br />\n<br />\n不如轉戰打民意 宣揚Love and peace!!（對市民）<br />\n<br />\n呢個係小弟愚見，大家都可以發表你地既睇法<br />\n<br />\n香港人 要進化，進步呀！！！！（唔好俾呢到啲仇恨主義沖昏頭腦！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個上前線上到無力既人上<br />\n<br />\n（係其他po推得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ:而家戴gear唔驚俾狗圍？<br />\nA:狗隻問咪答佢 宣揚愛與和平同化武危害 （實際真係無擾民）得個19口罩/豬咀 真係咬唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34131e7f101ad78c1f5a33fe38f944e05bf6dfa","tid":1742911,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=54f09491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=2cf9bfe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=33371b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=30f23e07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"e6e59bf266f9daae38b195eb9ede8e7044a3db5a","tid":1742911,"uid":258967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"just no sorry, <br />\n用返roadblock既取易不取難既concept既話。<br />\n就係用當我地比人捉晒，我們會讀完書然後去美國，以後香港既數十年就要靠你們了，能否退休就看你們自己了，加油，等等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e149673c27440ed9009a75594aa1db01c4e1a","tid":1742911,"uid":124128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:50:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f195ddf62332c73ebb20e6aa88c275cc9a7f0135","tid":1742911,"uid":124128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:50:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"098d37d5b84cd93377fe863eb83425a906e36d85","tid":1742911,"uid":124128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:50:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7994c802a75777785e951971222eecb2636500df","tid":1742911,"uid":124128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:51:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eea6f630130d994ab55e60a861dfa544c9